  "instructions": [
    "Preheat vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine flour and baking powder. Add water and mix until dough forms.",
    "Form the dough into small balls and flatten them slightly using your hands to create bun shapes.",
    "Fry each bread roll in hot oil for about 1-2 minutes or until golden brown on both sides.",
    "Remove from heat and let it cool before adding sesame seeds. Toss gently so they stick evenly.",
    "Serve immediately while still warm."
